item.title: Master Plan: Part 1
item.description: This blog documents progress of my medium-term master plan: Learn to program robots: Self-Drivng Car Engineer, Robotics Software Engineer, and Flying Car and Autonomous Flight Engineer Learn basic electronics: Electronic Engineering Technology Get a better job, assembling electronics. Learn to operate and maintain industrial robots: Controls Engineering Technology Get a better job, maintaining industrial robots. Gain experience. Move to Texas. Get a job with Tesla in Austin or SpaceX in Boca Chica.
